        <abstract> 
<p>CD has made clear that in <hi rend="italic">Cross and self-fertilisation</hi> he had not intended to suggest that <hi rend="italic">autogamie</hi> (fertilisation of a flower by its own pollen) is superior to <hi rend="italic">gitonogamie</hi> (fertilisation of a flower by one on the same plant).</p> 
